data.name: antimalwarelabel.Text
data.value:
Malware Scan will perform a rapid scan within memory and most known locations where usually malwares are hiding. Please note this scan doesn't mean you are 100% safe, and also, to avoid abuse, this will not remove them automatic, you will have then to remove them manually or with a deep Antivirus Scan.
Startup Scan will automatically check whether in your startup applications there are some suspicious entries. You will still have then to remove them manually or with the help of an Antivirus.

data.name: ransomwaredescriptions.Text
data.value: Make sure you config the vault. PCNukerPro will try to protect your folders from reading and writing if a suspicious activity is detected. It's always recommended not to turn on the PC when a ransomware flag is being raised and to analyze the drive from another Computer (RescueDisk, SysRescue)
